data.text: Lane College is a private nonprofit institution located in Jackson, TN. The school has... approximately 1095 undergraduate students. The school offers students degree opportunities. The average family income of students that are attending this school is $22,208. The average age of students entering Lane College is 21. The most popular programs at the Lane College are: Business, Management, Marketing, And Related Support Services (26%), Biological And Biomedical Sciences (15%), Social Sciences (13%), Communication, Journalism, And Related Programs (11%) and Homeland Security, Law Enforcement, Firefighting And Related Protective Services (10%).
